S'The official HotUKDeals.com app is your access to deals, voucher codes, freebies and savings right on your mobile device. Join our community of over 600,000 UK consumers who freely share discounts and tips that often aren\'t advertised in stores or flyers. Never pay retail again! HUKD mobile helps you: \xe2\x80\x93 View the hottest deals our community voted as \'Hot!\' \xe2\x80\x93 Discover local deals (both online and in store) that HUKD members have found in your current area. \xe2\x80\x93 Search our database for up to date, member shared voucher codes from trusted retailers like Asda, Dominos Pizza, Tesco, Sainsburys, Argos, Zavvi, and more. \xe2\x80\x93 Learn about deals you\'re interested in finding, as they are posted. HUKD keyword alerts allow you to enter a descriptive word like \xe2\x80\x9cdvd\xe2\x80\x9d, \xe2\x80\x9cHeinz beans\xe2\x80\x9d or \xe2\x80\x9cps3\xe2\x80\x9d and get a notification when new deals match your interests. If you have a specific store in mind, HUKD mobile also allows you to filter offers by merchant to narrow your browsing. For example, gadget fiends can find the hottest electronics deals from ebuyer, Amazon, Currys, PC World with a single tap. Looking for advice before you make a product purchase? Sign up with HUKD to give and get genuine advice on deals, merchants, products, services and more. Interact with the HUKD Community: \xe2\x80\x93 Comment on any member\xe2\x80\x99s shared hot deal, voucher code or question. \xe2\x80\x93 Submit deals or tips as you find them \xe2\x80\x93 Rate other members\xe2\x80\x99 deals by voting hot or cold. You can also follow the activity on deals you posted and keep up to date with your favourite HUKD users. Keep track of updates to deals, comments, and votes made by users in your Activity Feed. Feel like sharing a bargain with friends and family? Share deals you find over Facebook, Twitter, email or SMS text message. Hundreds of hidden deals are being posted everyday, so don\'t miss out. Install the app and get Hooked on Hot UK Deals.Recent changes:\xc2\xb7 Redesigned user login and sign up process..\xc2\xb7 When browsing through a long list of deals, the app navigation will slide away.\xc2\xb7 Looking to quickly browse between the hottest deals? Just swipe side to side to quickly change the deal type.\xc2\xb7 Recognize when a great deal got away by looking out for the "expired" message.\xc2\xb7 Want to follow up with a thread from your Activity tab? Tapping on a comment will now take you right to that location.\xc2\xb7 Various stability and speed improvements.'
